title: Equipment for the production of polyethylene bags for agriculture purpose US-SJ-100/FM2000

short_description: This US-SJ-100/FM2000 model equipment, mainly adapted to the production of agricultural polyethylene bags, has a production capacity of 80 kg to 160 kg per hour. The total power of the equipment is 110 kW, the shaft diameter is 100 mm, the film thickness is 0.02-0.10 mm, the weight is 7600 kg, and the total size is 8.0 * 3.5 * 8.5 m. Other models of this equipment are also shown in the description, and their prices differ depending on the model.

Uskunaning umumiy quvvati 110 kW, val diametri 100 mm, plyonka qalinligi 0.02-0.10 mm, vazni 7600 kg va umumiy o'lchami  esa 8.0 * 3.5 * 8.5 m ni tashkil etadi. Tavsifda shu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ularning narxlari modellariga qarab farqlanadi.
